<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🤝 QA Platform</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= @first_name %>,</h2>
      
      <p>You have been invited to join our <strong>QA Platform</strong> as a <strong><%= @role.humanize %></strong>.</p>
      
      <p>Our platform helps teams manage:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>📋 Test Cases & Test Management</li>
        <li>🎫 Issue Tracking & Bug Reports</li>
        <li>🤖 Automation Scripts & Execution</li>
        <li>📊 Analytics & Reporting</li>
        <li>👥 Team Collaboration</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Click the button below to accept your invitation and get started:</p>
      
      <a href="<%= @invitation_link %>" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
      
      <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p><%= @invitation_link %></p>
      
      <p>This invitation was sent by <strong><%= @inviter_name %></strong>.</p>
      
      <p>Welcome to the team!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2024 QA Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>